(define/contract (maximum-sum-of-heights maxHeights)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let* ([n (length maxHeights)]
         [left (make-vector n)]
         [right (make-vector n)]
         [sum 0])
    ;; Initialize the left and right vectors
    (vector-set! left 0 (list-ref maxHeights 0))
    (vector-set! right (- n 1) (list-ref maxHeights (- n 1)))
    ;; Update left vector
    (for ([i (in-range 1 n)])
      (vector-set! left i (min (vector-ref left (- i 1)) (list-ref maxHeights i))))
    ;; Update right vector
    (for ([i (in-range (- n 2) -1 -1)])
      (vector-set! right i (min (vector-ref right (+ i 1)) (list-ref maxHeights i))))
    ;; Calculate the maximum sum of heights
    (for ([i (in-range n)])
      (set! sum (+ sum (min (vector-ref left i) (vector-ref right i)))))
    sum))
